## v1.3.0 — 2026-04-21

**Amendment**: Added all-clean direct execution, cherry=1 rebase-merge artifact handling,
and remove-worktree-keep-branch pattern for closed-not-merged PRs.

- Added "All-clean worktrees allow direct execution" block to When to Use with detection
  command to check all dirty counts in one pass
- Added Phase 0 full decision-matrix inventory command (worktree + branch + ahead + dirty +
  staged + cherry + PR state) — complete triage in a single loop, no back-and-forth
- Added "cherry=1 rebase-merge artifact" note in Phase 1 with classification shell snippet:
  cherry=1 on MERGED PR = rebase artifact (safe to remove); cherry=1 on CLOSED/NO_PR = real
  unreleased work
- Added Phase 1.5 "Classify Closed-Not-Merged PRs" with remove-worktree-keep-branch as the
  correct default when a branch has unique commits but its PR was CLOSED without merging
- Added cherry=1 rebase-merge row to Failed Attempts table
- Added 17-worktree direct-execution row to Scale reference table
- Added ProjectOdyssey verification row to Verified On table

